OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779134802
OL,3,CCelebrations for the Irish cattle
OL,4,Cwhich saw off possible extinction
OL,6,FBy Nathan Hylands
OL,8,FThere have been double celebrations at
OL,9,FBalmoral Show for the owner of a cow
OL,10,Ffrom Northern Ireland's only surviving
OL,11,Fnative cattle breed.
OL,13,FMichelle McCauley said it is "super
OL,14,Fspecial" to take home the Irish Moiled
OL,15,Fchampionship while also marking a
OL,16,Fcentenary since the breed established
OL,17,Fa record of ancestry, known as a
OL,18,Fherdbook.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
