PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779134802
OL,3,CCelebrations for the Irish cattle
OL,4,Cwhich saw off possible extinction
OL,6,FThe Irish Moiled, known as one of the
OL,7,Frarest and most distinctive cattle
OL,8,Fbreeds, was traditionally used for its
OL,9,Fmilk but more recently it has been
OL,10,Ffarmed for beef.
OL,12,FThe cattle found home in counties
OL,13,FTyrone, Armagh, Donegal and Sligo
OL,14,Fduring the early 1900's.
OL,16,FHowever, in the 1980s the breed was
OL,17,Fclose to extinction with only around
OL,18,F20 females and two males surviving.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779134802
OL,3,CCelebrations for the Irish cattle
OL,4,Cwhich saw off possible extinction
OL,6,FMs McCauley "fell in love" with the
OL,7,Fcattle and has been breeding them for
OL,8,F15 years.
OL,10,FThe Dungannon breeder won the Irish
OL,11,FMoiled champion with her cow named
OL,12,F'Burren Royal Pandora'.
OL,14,FMichelle said to win on the 100th
OL,15,Fanniversary was "absolutely special".
OL,17,F"I am over the moon. This is the
OL,18,F'Pandora' cow family, which has been
OL,19,Fvery successful," she said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779134802
OL,3,CCelebrations for the Irish cattle
OL,4,Cwhich saw off possible extinction
OL,6,F"This lady, this is her fourth time at
OL,7,FBalmoral. She got champion last year,
OL,8,Fso it was a tall order to come back
OL,9,Fagain."
OL,11,F'The cow your great-great-grandparents
OL,12,Fwould have had'
OL,14,FSpeaking about the breed over the last
OL,15,Fcentury, Michelle said: "They haven't
OL,16,Fevolved. A lot of the other breeds,
OL,17,Fespecially native breeds, have got
OL,18,Fbigger.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779134802
OL,3,CCelebrations for the Irish cattle
OL,4,Cwhich saw off possible extinction
OL,6,F"She's the same type of cow that our
OL,7,Fgreat-great-grandparents would have
OL,8,Fhad on the farm."
OL,10,F"They are very suitable for
OL,11,Fconservation grazing because they
OL,12,Fdon't poach the ground," she added.
OL,14,F"They're great foragers`they encourage
OL,15,Fthat biodiversity, the growth of
OL,16,Fwildflowers, because they're nibbling
OL,17,Fon that."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779134802
OL,3,CCelebrations for the Irish cattle
OL,4,Cwhich saw off possible extinction
OL,6,FMichelle said the work to conserve the
OL,7,Fbreed is ongoing as it is listed as
OL,8,F'at risk' by the Rare Breeds Survival
OL,9,FTrust.
OL,11,FTo allow the breed to thrive, Michelle
OL,12,Fsaid breeders "can't sit back".
OL,14,FLooking to the future she said: "I
OL,15,Fwould like to be saying we have double
OL,16,Fthe heifer (female) calf
OL,17,Fregistrations."
OL,19,F"We would love to see the breed keep
OL,20,Fgoing. We have to keep working, keep
OL,21,Fpromoting."
OL,26,@xD@LpmxD@Spn
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779134802
OL,3,CCelebrations for the Irish cattle
OL,4,Cwhich saw off possible extinction
OL,6,FCaroline and Ryan Maxwell from near
OL,7,FMarkethill have been breeding Irish
OL,8,FMoiled cattle from 2017.
OL,10,F"I bought a cow called Daisy at six
OL,11,Fmonths old from Robert Boyle in
OL,12,FMillisle. She was the foundation of
OL,13,Fthe herd," Caroline said.
OL,15,FShe likes the breed because of their
OL,16,Fnature and "unique red and white look,
OL,17,Fand their markings".
OL,19,FShowing on the 100th year of the breed
OL,20,Fhas "got something special about it,"
OL,21,Fshe added.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779134802
OL,3,CCelebrations for the Irish cattle
OL,4,Cwhich saw off possible extinction
OL,6,FThe Maxwell's young female 'Delilah'
OL,7,Fwon her class and their young male was
OL,8,Fsecond. Both of them together achieved
OL,9,Freserve champion pair.
OL,11,F'A very big family affair'
OL,13,FCaroline said: "Balmoral is the
OL,14,Fbiggest event of the year. I would
OL,15,Fnever miss it. Growing up we always
OL,16,Fcame with horses, sheep, poultry and
OL,17,Fthen started with the cattle.
OL,19,FThe mother-of-two said her children
OL,20,F"are a wee bit young at the minute" to
OL,21,Fshow cattle.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779134802
OL,3,CCelebrations for the Irish cattle
OL,4,Cwhich saw off possible extinction
OL,6,F"Hopefully in another four or five
OL,7,Fyears they'll be useful to give a
OL,8,Fhelping hand. Even my father and my
OL,9,Fsister`everybody shows something in
OL,10,Fthe family."
OL,12,FShe said in the future she would "love
OL,13,Fto breed the overall champion" at
OL,14,FBalmoral Show.
OL,16,FCaroline described the future of the
OL,17,Fbreed as "definitely looking bright"
OL,18,Fwith society events throughout the
OL,19,Fyear to mark the anniversary.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
