PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779134802
OL,3,CCelebrations for the Irish cattle
OL,4,Cwhich saw off possible extinction
OL,6,FOver 100,000 visitors are expected to
OL,7,Fdescend on Balmoral Park across four
OL,8,Fdays. There are numerous livestock
OL,9,Fcompetitions and equestrian events
OL,10,Falongside activities for families.
OL,12,FYou can experience all the sights,
OL,13,Fsounds and smells from the Balmoral
OL,14,FShow 2026 by watching 'UTV at the
OL,15,FShow' which will air on Sunday 24th
OL,16,FMay.
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/15
